data.description: Beautifully remodeled home with spectacular mountain and valley views. A spacious 3 bedroom, two bath on one level with new kitchen, upgraded bathrooms, manufactured flooring, ceiling fans throughout and efficient pellet stove.  New furnace, water heater and holding tank. Well was recently deepened with new pump. New driveway, roof replaced and freshly painted so you can move right in and enjoy this country home.  Barn/Shop is ready for your toys or horses. Desirable Washoe Valley home is conveniently located between Carson City and Reno. Room for Rv's/boats and plenty of space to turn around on the property.
